Tests are conducted only in cases where the age of the person is doubtful.
According to Johan Gjoranssona of the forensic Medicine Agency, the results are consistent with the results of the previous months.
"We do not see much difference with the statistics for the past months, the numbers are quite appropriate," he said to the portal "the Local".
