Then it was decided to make more efficient use of these contacts, to create a contact group.
Its task is to analyze the situation, identify key factors and players, and dialogue with all parties to the conflict.
I want to emphasize: in Libya we do not want to be associated with any of the parties to the conflict, we are engaged in dialogue with all.
How many people are in the contact group and how many of them are permanently in Libya?
Now the contact group consists of five people.
