We hope that the parties will reach compromise solutions and achieve an internal consensus.
Then we have to pass the elections, which was discussed at the meeting of Saradzha and Haftara.
If the elections are held and the legitimate authority is finally elected (and now none of the parties has such status), it is possible to put in the UN un the issue of lifting the arms embargo.
