National trade union of unskilled, municipal and boiler workers (GMB) concerned about investment in the Mcvitie's factory in Glasgow
The trade union demands guarantees from the managers of biscuit manufacturer Mcvitie's in connection with its long-term commitment to manufacture at the plant in Glasgow.
